race.comment: LEKTRA SKIP (6) got around the 410m at this track to take a Grade 5 in a sharp 23.28 for a 5 length win. Should be in this for a long way. ALL MUCKED UP (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (26.15) last time in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. TAKE THE STEPS (4) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (28.03) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can feature with the right run. PAW OLYSLAGERS (1) placed last start and is in the mix again.
